<h3>Overview</h3>
<p>This tab content was loaded from the server via HTMX. Each tab triggers an <code>hx-get</code> request to fetch its content, while Alpine.js manages the active tab state on the client.</p>
<p class="text-muted text-sm mt-1">The tab panel uses <code>hx-target</code> to swap only the content area, keeping the tab bar interactive.</p>
